<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4283765>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 5. Morphological variation of retrostylets in vaigamid genera. A Gamispatulus schizodontis Thatcher & Boeger, 1984 from Thatcher & Boeger (1984a), with spatulate process (seta). B Gamispinus diabolicus Thatcher & Boeger, 1984 from Thatcher & Boeger (1984b). C Gamidactylus piranhus Thatcher, Santos & Brasil-Sato, 2008 from Thatcher et al. (2008). D Vaigamus retrobarbatus Thatcher & Robertson, 1984 from Thatcher & Robertson (1984), with innermost portion extending posteriorly (seta). E Pseudovaigamus spinicephalus (Thatcher & Robertson, 1984) from Thatcher & Robertson (1984), with innermost portion extending posteriorly (seta). F Pseudovaigamus tridentatus n. sp., with innermost portion extending posteriorly (seta). Scale bars in µm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4283765/files/figure.png" .

